data.value: Step 3 : • Fill up the informations needed. • Choose if Core Curriculum, Applied Track, or Specialized / Major the Subject is. • Check the subjects you already taken and put your Grades in every Semester. • Click "Preview" if you want to see the output. • Click "Print" if you want to have a hardcopy of the output. • Click "Reset" to remove the informations you already put.
